high_descs: Turn around and walk to the grey sofa.
Pick up the knife from the couch.
Turn around and walk to the bedroom on the left to reach the bed.
Cut the potato on the bed into slices with the knife.
Put the knife on the bed.
Pick up a potato from the bed.
Turn around and head out the room on the left and turn right to enter the dining room to reach the fridge on the left.
Cool the slice of potato in the fridge and take it out.
Turn around to reach the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the cold potato in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right, walk across the room, and go to the grey colour sofa
Pick the knife from the couch.
Turn around, walk towards the TV across the room, and hang a left, then go to the bedroom, and walk to the bed with the potato.
Choose the potato next to the kettle and make it slices using the knife.
Put the knife on the bed near the side table.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn around and go back to the living room to your left and hang a right, then walk into the dining room, and go to the fridge to your left.
Put the potato in the lower shelf of the fridge, close the door of the fridge, then wait for a moment and get the potato slice out of the fridge.
Turn around to your backside towards the microwave.
Put the potato slice into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Cut a Potato into slices and put a slice into the Microwave

high_descs: Turn around, turn left. Continue to the sofa.
Grab the knife.
Turn around, go to the wall and turn left. Go inside and turn right. Go to the bed.
Cut the potato twice.
Place the knife at the bottom left of the bed.
Grab a potato.
Leave the room. Turn left, continue and when you reach the next entrance, turn right. Enter the room and stand in front of the fridge.
Open the refrigerator. Place the potato piece on the left side. Close the refrigerator. Open the refrigerator for 6 seconds. Take out the potato piece. Close the refrigerator.
Turn back.
Open the microwave. Place the potato piece on the left side. Close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Cut a piece of potato. Cool it and place it in a microwave oven.
